Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami?\N--We've been had...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our treasure is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Pirate Ship Disappears!\NFortress Battle, Round #2"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting away! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lt. Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are shallow waters, and we\Nhave to go through the shore reef,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so all this smoke is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of that! And I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if they make it onto the ocean outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wind up the laughingstock\Nand shame of the entire navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We-- the Navarone Fortress-- will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Those damn navy\Nbigwigs'll start arguing again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about destroying some useless\Nhedgehog of a fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that can't even capture a\Nsingle bug that snuck inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! As a marine of the Navarone\NFortress, can you tolerate that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all warships!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead! Pass through the Sea Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the outside ocean! We can\Nget out if we go straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, we can't leave!\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the ship back! Turn it around! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back into the fortress!\NThe navy stole all our gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you insane, Nami?!\NWe almost died trying to get this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do make it out,\Nthere's no point without the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When money is involved,\Nshe can be strangely persuasive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love that side of Nami-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we made that huge hole!\NWhy can't we just leave now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aren't we pirates, Luffy?!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think pirates leaving\Ngold behind is shameful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right rudder, full! Make a U-turn\Nand take us back into the fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right! Got it!\N--Yes! As you wish, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right rudder, full!\N--U-turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold on, you guys!\N--What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, that's it! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound the alarm bell! Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see a thing in this smoke!\NBe sure not to hit any fellow ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind chimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are alarm bells for signaling\Nyour location to other ships in fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! One's coming straight at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that? Is that good enough, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Left rudder, full!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--We have to change course or we'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you want, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We almost wound up in pieces\Nwithout ever seeing the gold again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Not again...\N--There are lots more wind chimes than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one-- two-- no, even more\Nwarships coming from the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! What'll it be? Left or right rudder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get out of this smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what she says!\NShe's the best navigator in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, God...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going straight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out of this dangerous\Nsmoke as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna spot us, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We'll be sitting ducks\Nonce we leave the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get blasted and wind up\Nat the bottom of the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to play it by ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Navigator...\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did some research in the reference room--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:08:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this fortress actually used to house\Nmany more people and warships.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Robin! This is no time for old stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was military downsizing.\NThey've really fallen into decline since.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems there are many\Nunused docks in this port.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unused docks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That's some nice info, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We're gonna hide the\NGoing Merry in an old dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! And where exactly is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the cannoneers at the waterway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask if the Straw Hat ship passed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, cannoneers! This is Drake's flagship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the Straw Hats' ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, no other ships have\Npassed through the Sea Gate yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you disappear to, pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you managed\Nto sneak past the cannoneers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and vanish beyond the horizon\Nin that short period of time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost sight of the pirate ship\Nonce it entered the outer waters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as if they\Nmagically turned invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sir?!\N--No, good work. Come on back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk leisurely about\Nour forthcoming plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't try to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with their dreams still in this fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna be court-martialed\Nfor insulting a superior officer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that? He's gonna court-martial us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! Be our guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two! Let that man go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Major Shepherd, special\Ninspector for Navy Command!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say the Straw Hats are right around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to use them a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll wait for them\Nto come out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Straw Hat pirates\Nhave us working like crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:11:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for some good, energizing grub,\Nthen it's back to searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! This isn't\Nlike this morning's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'd never had anything like it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be skimpin'! Give us\Nsome grub like this morning's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us good food! Give us good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica-san! The soldiers are\Ncomplaining about their meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us good food! Give us good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us use those recipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where has your pride as\Ncooks of Navarone gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he was a pirate,\Nbut he was still an excellent cook
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who made food for the famished\Nsoldiers who came here to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! All these men want to be\Nrevitalized by eating his food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make a decision! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Jessica-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will make our own cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's every bit as delicious\Nand replenishing as his!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for today, we'll abandon our\Ncheap pride and borrow his recipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that he wasn't a pirate\Nin the kitchen-- he was a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's most important of all\Nis satisfying the people eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you standing around for?!\NThose men are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now, Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should go back to the\Ngate and get onto the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! These guys mean business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame about the gold,\Nbut our lives are more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the gold! But I'm hungry! Sanji! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for some food\Nand make you somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storeroom is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be something left somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think it's okay to\Nescape without getting the gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a pity.\NPirate treasure is always divided up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And given all that gold, we'd each\Nhave gotten so much money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Divided up?!\N--Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!\NI'm gonna buy me a bronze statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Can we buy books?!\NI want the latest medical books!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to study all sorts of medical\Ntechniques I don't know about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New pots and frying pans,\Nplus silverware and giant mousetraps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves a crapload left over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could drink all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right?!\N--Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, my stash will be 80%!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:14:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously! You can't just\Nopenly have a secret stash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By "stash," I mean money\Nsaved up to repair the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship? You mean Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The Going Merry is\Nwhat brought us where we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it has given us a ride on the seas\Never since my East Blue village...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a slightly older model,\Nbut I personally designed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A carvel-make caravel, with lateen\Nsails and a central stern rudder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get on already.\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! I'm the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:15:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made so many memories with this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of leaving this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was with us when we\Ncrossed Reverse Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and burst onto the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean really is flowing up it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going into the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it! This is the greatest sea\Nin the world! The Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Piece is up ahead, somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the sky islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this ship's navigator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men! Do what Nami-san says!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! The ship is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! You're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I even risked my life to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't harm the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then someone fixed the ship for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it,\Nthis ship's been through a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done so much for us,\Nbut now it's all beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! The Going Merry's Great Repair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. Since we don't\Nknow how much it'll cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll hold off on dividing up\Nthe treasure when we get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took most of the food,\Nbut not the stuff in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Usopp's cheap repairs\Nare just about at their limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know that I'm a sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, Mechao-san said the\Nsame thing-- that it needs real repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We should go to a real shipbuilding dock
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have real shipwrights fix it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people better than\Nyou at fixing ships, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you gotta take extra good care,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or you'll wind up paying for it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a shipwright in our crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our journey is far from over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need those skills anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Merry is our home! Our life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a shipwright who can keep it safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, on rare occasion,\Nhe gets straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best way! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, then that's the plan!\N--I hope we find someone good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we need a musician, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to be all excited, but have\Nyou forgotten what comes first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--We have to get our gold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question is, where's it hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a vault, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that! The problem is,\Nwe don't know where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hafta yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a guess, but if I were\Nto hide gold in this fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this multi-lock storage vault\Nseems like the only place to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--You're so smart, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that does seem the most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys! Let's go there\Nand get our gold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are we just gonna leave the\NGoing Merry here? It'll get spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hide a tree in a forest! Hide a ship in ships!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't try to get too serious that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the remains of a dock\Nwhere ships were built and repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we came in just now, I saw\Nplenty of abandoned materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisper, whisper, whisper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?! Help me out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:21:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least now we don't have to\Nworry about it being stolen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gluing paper all over the\NGoing Merry was a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I dunno how long it'll fool people,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,given how crappily it's been done...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! This is definitely a navy\Nwarship, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Now to get our gold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! We commence\Ntonight at midnight! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why don't we go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the mood'll be\Nbetter at night, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mood! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think that's quite why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush forth, rush forth,\Non the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in, we won't give in,\Neven if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be scared of,\Nwe can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we don't have to worry\Nabout Merry, but hold on, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just gonna go like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Seven people running\Naround will stand out too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I'll give you my super secret plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--On the next One Piece!\N--I do this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Gold and Waver Recovery Operations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
